  Soe3-kiaN2.“Goa2 beh lai5 khi3 chhe7 chit8 e5 thiN-sai3! Goa2 beh tui3 toa7 lou7 tit8-tit8 chau2 lai5 khi3, kau3 goa2 chhe7-tioh8 chiah soah.” 
