  Soe3-kiaN2.“Goa2 taN m7-si7 soe3-han3! Goa2 u7 chheng7-khou3; taN si7 toa7-han3 lah.” 
  Lau7-bu2.“Ah, u7 iaN2 houN3. Goa2 soa3 boe7 ki3-tit, chong2--si7 chiah ho2 thiN, goa2 ia7 ai3 chhut-khi3 san3-pou7 cheh.” 
  Soe3-kiaN2.“Chong2--si7 li2 pai2-kha, kiaN5-tioh8 hiah ban7.” 
