  Sou2-i2 in chiu7 khi2-sin, gin2-a2 na2 chau2 na2 thiau3, lau7-bu2 ia7 chhun kha tit8-tit8 chin3-cheng5, ti3-kau3 gin2-a2 liam5-piN boe7 ki3-tit i si7 pai2-kha. 
  Gin2-a2 chin3-cheng5 kiaN5, chiu7 khoaN3-kiN3 ti7 i bin7-cheng5 chit8 chiah peh8-be2 thoa be2-chhia teh lai5. Lai7-bin7 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 kui3 hu7-jin5 teh che7, chheng7 tiu5-toan7, ia7 u7 peh8 e5 chiau2-mng5 ti7 i ou-sim3-sim3 e5 thau5-mng5-teng2 teh iaN7. I teh tin2-tang7 e5 si5, i sou2 chng-thaN7 e5 po2-chioh8 kap kim-khi3 tit8-tit8 sih, chong2--si7 i hit nng7 lui2 bak8-chiu pi2 hiah e5 kim-kong-chioh8 koh-khah kng. 
